headline: Figma Announces Pricing of Initial Public Offering
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, July 30, 2025--Tomorrow, July 31, 2025, Figma plans to begin trading on the New York Stock Exchange under the ticker symbol "FIG."

headline: SoFi Technologies, Inc. Announces Pricing of Public Offering of Common Stock
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, July 30, 2025--SoFi Technologies, Inc. (NASDAQ: SOFI) ("SoFi" or the "Company") today announced that it has priced its previously announced underwritten public offering of 71,942,450 shares of its common stock at a price of $20.85 per share, for total gross proceeds of approximately $1.5 billion, before deducting underwriting discounts and commissions and offering expenses payable by the company.
